import React from 'react'
import { Container, DishType, SpicyLogo, TypeDiv, VeganLogo, VegitarianLogo } from './StyleSignatures'

export default function DesktopSignatureDishOf() {
  return (
    <Container Mobile={false}>
       <DishType>THE MEANING OF OUR ICONS: </DishType>
        <TypeDiv>
            <SpicyLogo/>
            <DishType>Spicy</DishType>
        </TypeDiv>

        <TypeDiv>
            <VegitarianLogo/>
            <DishType>Vegitarian</DishType>
        </TypeDiv>

        <TypeDiv>
            <VeganLogo/>
            <DishType>Vegan</DishType>
        </TypeDiv> 

    </Container>

  )
}
